    <div class="allianceSection collapsable collapsed">
        <h4 class="header">Regional Status</h4>
        
            <p>Stands occur primarily on the Modoc Plateau (Geographical Information Center, in progress), but the distribution of this alliance is likely more widespread. Based on Calflora and CCH records as well as proximity to subsections with mapped stands, there are likely unmapped stands of the alliance in subsections of the Mono (341Dk), Northwestern Basin and Range (342Be), Southern Cascades (M261Dd, i, j, m), and Sierra Nevada (M261Eb, d, i).</p>
        

        <ul class="text">
        
            <li><b>Modoc Plateau</b> (M261Gb-d, Gf-p). Mapped stands occur throughout the Modoc Plateau except in major valleys (Pit River/Warm Springs Valleys - M261Gg, Big Valley - M261Go, and Fall River Valley - M261Gp). While much of the land within these valleys is likely too low in elevation or too developed for the alliance, there are small areas in which stands can be expected to occur.</li>
        
            <li><b>Mono</b> (341Dk). No description available</li>
        
            <li><b>Northwestern Basin and Range</b> (342Bd-e). Stands are present at the western edges of the Cottonwood - Skedaddle Mountains subsection.</li>
        
            <li><b>Sierra Nevada</b> (M261Ea-d, Ei-j). No description available</li>
        
            <li><b>Southern Cascades</b> (M261Dd, Dh-j, Dm). No description available</li>
        
        </ul>
    </div>


    
	
<div class="allianceSection collapsable collapsed">
	 <h4 class="header">Management Considerations</h4>
	<div class="text"> Sites hosting this alliance are often too dry to support a closed tree canopy forest. Many stands have a history of livestock grazing which tends to reduce grass cover and favors shrub and tree establishment. Vegetation of this alliance can be too widely spaced to carry fire, but mixed fire regimes and variable return intervals for surface fires maintain the typical patchy, shrub-dominated understory (NatureServe 2019). </div>
</div>

    

    

    <div class="allianceSection collapsable collapsed">
